onstraints. This move, welcomed by apartment residents and federations, aims to enhance transparency and accountability for millions living in apartments across the state.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/karnataka-to-enact-kaoma-ordinance-for-vertical-growth-in-apartment-living/129836850?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-29142/129836850.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}]}